<HEADLINE> People's Daily Hails Success of NPC Session (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The revised Constitution will have an important and far-
reaching significance to the Chinese people's efforts to hold
higher the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory, rally more
closely around the CPC Central Committee with Jiang Zemin at its
core, adhere to the Party's basic line at the primary stage of
socialism, and build China into a modernized socialist country
which is prosperous, powerful, democratic and has highly developed
culture and ethics, it adds.
</P>
<P>
The editorial goes on to say that the most important thing at
present is to implement the NPC session's guidelines and
arrangements, and guide all officials and people to concentrate on
and work enthusiastically for the accomplishment of various tasks
set forth by the central authorities.
</P>
<P>
"We must continue to promote reforms and opening-up, make a
great effort to implement the strategy of invigorating the nation
through science and education and the strategy of sustainable
development, take expanding the domestic demand as the major
measure to drive the economic growth, stabilize and strengthen
agricultural work, deepen the reform of the state enterprises, do
a good job of the financial reform so as to prevent and defuse
financial crisis, readjust economic structure and straighten out
the economic order, maintain the sustainable, fast and healthy
development of the national economy, intensify our efforts to
promote the building of democratic legal system and the cultural
and ethic progress," it says.
</P>
<P>
"We must ensure social and political stability, promote a
comprehensive social advancement, and strive for outstanding
achievements in the reform, opening-up and socialist modernization
drive, so as to greet the 50th founding anniversary of the People'
s Republic of China and Macao's return to the motherland," it
urges.  
</P>
</TEXT>
