The MD-80 plane, which left Seoul Kimpo Airport around 10:55 a.
m. and was scheduled to land in Pohang around 11:30 a.m., cracked
its central part and partially damaged its wings after it strayed
off the runway and skidded through a wire fence some 140 meters.
</P>
<P>
