a "most serious warning" over revelations that he had accepted
free travel receptions to the United States from 2002 Winter
Olympic Games bidders Salt Lake City.
</P>
<P>
New South Wales state premier Bob Carr became the latest of
officials and politicians who had urged Coles to resign from the
board.
</P>
<P>
