<HEADLINE> Ukraine Trims Government </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, March 14 (Xinhua) -- Ukrainian President Leonid Kuchma on
Sunday hacked the existing 21 government ministries to 18 to
improve administration and increase efficiency.
</P>
