<HEADLINE> Southern China Spending Heavily On Agriculture </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANNING, March 15 (Xinhua) -- China's Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous
Region will increase water-control construction work to give a
push to agriculture this year.
</P>
<P>
