last year, according to local authorities. Priority will be given
to dykes and dams in the cities of Nanning, Liuzhou, Wuzhou, and
Guilin and to 50 km. of embankments along the coast, improving 7
large reservoirs, and dredging 50 km. of rivers, authorities say.
