<HEADLINE> Chinese Scientists to Visit North Pole </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 15 (Xinhua) -- A second Chinese scientific
expedition team is scheduled to visit the North Pole in latter
half of this year.
</P>
<P>
