<HEADLINE> Chinese Premier to Meet Chinese, Overseas Press </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 15 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Premier Zhu Rongji will
meet both Chinese and overseas press here this afternoon at a
press conference sponsored by the Second Session of the Ninth
National People's Congress (NPC), China's top lawmaking body, and
answer their questions.
</P>
<P>
The press conference, scheduled at around 17:30 (Beijing time)
today in the Great Hall of the People where the NPC sits, will be
broadcast live by the Central People's Broadcasting Station, China
Central Television and China Radio International. 
</P>
</TEXT>
