<HEADLINE> Canada Wins Fifth Women's Ice Hockey World Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HELSINKI, March 14 (Xinhua) -- Canada saw off Olympic champions
United States 3-1 to win a fifth straight title in women's ice
hockey world championships in Espoo, Finland on Sunday night.
</P>
